<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an König Ruprecht I. </head><p>Der Rat kündigt Wilhelm Rummel, Bürger zu Nürnberg, wegen Beschlagnahmung vieler Waren Nürnberger Kaufleute im Gebiet Herzog Friedrichs IV. von Österreich an und bittet um gütliche Anhörung.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_99" id="48r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_99_r2l16">Kuͦnıg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_99_r2l17">Gnedıger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / vns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt etlıch <expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd <expan>kauffl<ex>eute</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l18">vvie daʒ Jn der <expan>hoch<ex>geporn</ex></expan> fürſt 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> hercʒog <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Oſter </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l19">
<del rend="strikethrough">reich </del> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Durc </del> Durchleuhtikeit tohterman / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> hercʒog </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l20"><expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Oſterreıch / etvvıeuil hab vnd kauffmanſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l21">in <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>herſchafte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd gepıeten bekümert hab / Darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l22">VVilhelm Rumell <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> künıgklıch <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> kümt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l23"> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ Jr </del> VVaʒ derſelb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> darümb an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> küniklıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l24">
<add><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></add> bringe / daʒ Jn <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> darynne gnedıklich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> / vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Jn </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l25">
<del rend="strikethrough">darümb </del> auſʒrichten wolle / durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>vvıllıge<ex>n</ex></expan> dinſt wıllen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_99_r2l26">Als vvir des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>kunıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnaden wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_99" id="48r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Kuͦnig </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        fürgelegt etlich <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und <expan>kauffl<ex>eute</ex></expan>, wie
                        daz in der <expan>hoch<ex>geporn</ex></expan> fürst,
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleuhtikeit tohterman,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                        Osterreich, etwievil hab und kauffmanschaft in
                            <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>herschafte<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        gepieten bekümert hab. Darümb Wilhelm Rumell, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> künigklich
                            <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> kümt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        waz derselb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> darümb an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        küniklich <add><expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></add> bringe, daz in
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> darynne gnediklich
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> und auszrichten wolle durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dinst willen, als wir des
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>kunikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnaden wol
                            <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
